c: 48
v: 15
t: "Nimujya gufata iminyago, abanze kujya ku rugamba bazavuga bati \"Reka tubakurikire.\" Barashaka guhindura amagambo ya Allah. Vuga \"Ntimudukurikire; uko ni ko Allah uti yavuze mbere.\" Hanyuma bazavuga bati \"Ahubwo mwatugiriye ishyari.\" Nyamara ntabwo bari basobanukiwe (ku bya Allah) uretse bike"